ablish and maintain social identities, how words can be used to embrace or push away, recognize or deny others, how conscious and unconscious biases play a role in the justice system resulting in unfair prison sentences skewed toward black people. Words have meaning and can be twisted to suit our individual beliefs and desires. There's so much to explore, dissect and discuss in this book, it will make you examine ideals and ask some tough questions. Retribution vs retaliation, right vs wrong, white vs black, it's all here and so much more.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eSome parts do read like you need to be at least a 2L law student with concepts going over my head but Jody Armour is a professor of law. Thank goodness for the internet.","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/9913646?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3473397066"},"likeCount":0,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v3.B23haLnvuF9bD4jt":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v3.B23haLnvuF9bD4jt","__typename":"Work","legacyId":81476978,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v3.OizWHseiOpRv91Be"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/81476978-n-gga-theory-race-language-unequal-justice-and-the-law","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/81476978-n-gga-theory-race-language-unequal-justice-and-the-law","publicationTime":null,"originalTitle":"","awardsWon":[],"places":[],"characters":[]},"reviews":{"__typename":"BookReviewsConnection","totalCount":17,"edges":[{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.tp15lyICTLS12KuBBrlt8A"}},{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.QSjMmfymH-yYMZt5tzwIGw"}},{